markets.title: Will Trump meet with Benjamin Netanyahu before 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If the President of the United States meets Benjamin Netanyahu from Mar 19, 2025 to May 1, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: A meeting will be included if the President and Benjamin Netanyahu shake hands or speak to each other directly; the President merely attending the same conference or event as Benjamin Netanyahu is not sufficient to resolve the market to Yes.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
